rows.label: tlk4140002802_msg0001
rows.name:
You're the ones who helped us back
there... Thank you. I think we made the
right decision thanks to your help.

rows.label: tlk4140002802_msg0002
rows.name:
Da was furious when he came back
at first, but in the end, he actually
approved of us getting married!

rows.label: tlk4140002802_msg0003
rows.name:
I imagine me running away from home
showed them just how serious I was
about all this.

rows.label: tlk4140002802_msg0004
rows.name:
I'm glad we worked up the courage to
go back to Trigo and face them.
